text = "[center]


[b][font_size=32]this game demo[/font_size][/b]
Author: me
License: All Rights Reserved



[b][font_size=32]Assets & Art[/font_size][/b]


[b][font_size=24]Models by Virtual Museums of Małopolska, used under CC-BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://sketchfab.com/WirtualneMuzeaMalopolski
Assets: Military hatchet model M1889;
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Models by ModeMorbase | Museu Virtual, used under CC-BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://sketchfab.com/carpetudo
Assets: Torre da Má Hora;
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Models by artfletch, used under CC-BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Assets: Lincoln's Inn Chapel Undercroft;
Link: https://sketchfab.com/artfletch
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Different material packs by Julio Sillet, used under CC-BY[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://juliosillet.gumroad.com/
Note: Slight modifications were made.


[b][font_size=24]Asset pack \"RTS medieval props\" by Lamoot, used under CC BY 3.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://opengameart.org/content/rts-medieval-props
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Asset pack \"Mega Lights Pack\" by burnedhrum, used under CC BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/mega-lights-pack-64f05bccecee49ebb7f26c5b949c92e3
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Asset pack \"LeversandSwitches\" by loafbrr, used under CC BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://loafbrr.itch.io/leversandswitches
Note: Modified from the original: retopology; UV wrapping; new materials


[b][font_size=24]Additional assets CC-By 4.0 GDQuest[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://www.gdquest.com
Notes: Shader materials were used: fire shader; sky shader. Modifications were made.


[b][font_size=24]Assets from tps-demo, used under CC-BY 3.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://github.com/godotengine/tps-demo
Notes: Shader materials were used: smoke. Modifications were made.


[b][font_size=24]Assets made by Blender Studio, used under CC-BY 4.0[/font_size][/b]
Link: https://studio.blender.org/welcome/
Notes: Materials from Charge Asset Library were used. Modifications were made.



