[b][font_size=24]Track: Siren Tarot (main menu theme)[/font_size][/b]
Author: me and noisedeception


[b][font_size=24]Track: Wave Paint 3[/font_size][/b]
Author: me


[b][font_size=24]Several environmental tracks (noise, bits, synths, melody)[/font_size][/b]
Author: me 


